Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:54.76,gatari,,0,0,0,,{\c&H003B6401\bord0\fn方正准雅宋_GBK\fsp8\rnd10\fs55\pos(604,352.2)}从车牌号码来判断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:54.80,gatari,,0,0,0,,{\c&H003B6401\bord0\fn方正准雅宋_GBK\fsp8\rnd10\fs55\pos(604,246.2)}从车牌号码来判断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:54.80,gatari,,0,0,0,,{\c&H003B6401\bord0\fn方正准雅宋_GBK\fsp8\rnd10\fs55\pos(664,526.2)}那应该是租借的轿车
